(556, 'Pulau Ubin and Chek Jawa', NULL, NULL, '', 'Pulau Ubin', NULL, 'Home to Singapore''s last villages or kampongs, the island still retains the rustic beauty and simplicity of a bygone era.', 'https://www.nparks.gov.sg/gardens-parks-and-nature/parks-and-nature-reserves/pulau-ubin-and-chek-jawa', NULL, 42465.2814, 43289.304, NULL, NULL, 'Parks', 'N'),
(557, 'Marina Bay Sands', NULL, NULL, '18956', 'Bayfront Avenue', NULL, 'Visit Singapore, stay at the Marina Bay Sands hotel and enjoy the Sands SkyPark and The Shoppes at Marina Bay Sands<sup>&reg;</sup>.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/family-fun/attraction/marina-bay-sands/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30936.7016, 29610.586, 'http://c1038.r38.cf3.rackcdn.com/group1/building2979/media/4c878c910e1377.79820853.jpg', '10', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(558, 'Sultan Mosque', NULL, NULL, '198833', 'Muscat Street', NULL, 'With its massive golden dome and huge prayer hall, the Sultan Mosque is one of Singapore&#39;s most imposing religious buildings, and the focal point of Muslims in Singapore.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/places-of-worship/sultan-mosque/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30865.8996, 31627.25, NULL, '3', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(559, 'Resorts World Sentosa', NULL, NULL, '99958', 'Artillery Avenue', NULL, 'Resort World Sentosa Singapore is located on Sentosa Island, where you can visit Universal Studios Singapore'' and stroll along FestiveWalk''. It is Asia''s ultimate destination, offering a whole new wor', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/family-fun/attraction/resorts-world-sentosa/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 27187.3849, 26207.853, NULL, '39', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(560, 'St Andrew''s Cathedral', NULL, NULL, '178959', 'St Andrews Road', NULL, 'Singapore''s largest cathedral was designed by Colonel Ronald MacPherson in 1856, a replacement of the original chapel which was destroyed by two lightning strikes in 1852.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/places-of-worship/st-andrews-cathedral/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30111.1323, 30572.138, NULL, '11', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(561, 'Singapore City Gallery', NULL, NULL, '69118', 'Maxwell Road', NULL, 'What if you don''t want to travel all the way to Sentosa''s Tiger Sky Tower to get a beautiful view on Singapore'' Some of the country''s best views are smack of the country bang right would be to come by', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/singapore-city-gallery.jpg', NULL, 29382.4034, 29183.535, NULL, '45', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(562, 'Merlion Park', NULL, NULL, '49213', 'Fullerton', NULL, 'Standing at 8.6 metres high and weighing 70 tonnes, the Merlion statue has a lion''s head and a fish''s body, and is housed here in this 2,500 square metre park.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/merlion-park.jpg', NULL, 30267.0581, 29759.303, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(563, 'Chinatown Heritage Centre', NULL, NULL, '59207', 'Pagoda Street', NULL, 'Relive the lives of the early Chinese migrants and learn more about Chinese culture in Singapore.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/chinatown-heritage-centre.jpg', NULL, 29224.5899, 29546.993, NULL, '48', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(564, 'Armenian Church', NULL, NULL, '179366', 'Hill Street', NULL, 'Take a walk in the lush gardens of the Armenian Church before entering the church and admire the exterior architecture.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/places-of-worship/armenian-church/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29819.3263, 30586.942, NULL, '60', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(565, 'Battle Box/ The Underground Command Centre', NULL, NULL, '179622', 'Cox Terrace', NULL, 'A bomb-proof complex that is capable of recycling its own air supply, you''ll be surrounded by sounds of bombing as you explore the Battle Box''s 22 chambers with your guide.<br/>', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/battle-box.jpg', NULL, 29421.4583, 30871.46, NULL, '2', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(566, 'Universal Studios Singapore', NULL, NULL, '98269', 'Sentosa Gateway', NULL, 'Ride The Movies at Universal Studios Singapore. Go beyond the screen and jump into the action from the state of the art rides such as Madagascar: A Crate Adventure, Shrek 4-D Adventure, Revenge of The', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/universal-studios.jpg', NULL, 26880.1054, 26359.342, NULL, '8', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(567, 'Haw Par Villa', NULL, NULL, '118628', 'Pasir Panjang Road', NULL, 'Haw Par Villa is like no other place in the world, with over 1,000 statues and 150 dioramas that dramatise Chinese legends and folklore.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/haw-par-villa.jpg', NULL, 22298.4621, 29725.073, NULL, '262', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(568, 'Butterfly Park & Insect Kingdom', NULL, NULL, '99702', 'Cable Car Road', NULL, 'This outdoor conservatory boasts more than 50 different species of butterflies, from the rare and endangered to the more common varieties.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/butterfly-park-and-insect-kingdom.jpg', NULL, 26204.3351, 26464.281, NULL, '51', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(569, 'Singapore Discovery Centre', NULL, NULL, '638365', 'Upper Jurong Road', NULL, 'The Singapore Discovery Centre''s mission is to inspire a desire in the locals to contribute to Singapore''s future, through the sharing of the Singapore Story in an interactive and interesting way.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/singapore-discovery-centre.jpg', NULL, 10840.1756, 35010.81, 'http://d20tdhwx2i89n1.cloudfront.net/image/upload/t_next_gen_article_large_767/dmehiezvh71nhalzfirm.jpg', '510', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(570, 'Kranji War Memorial', NULL, NULL, '738656', 'Woodlands Road', NULL, 'On your visit here at the Kranji War Memorial, you''ll see the war graves, the state cemetery, the memorial walls and the military graves.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/landmarks-and-memorials/kranji-war-memorial/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 19560.7024, 44534.561, NULL, '9', 'Tourist Attractions', 'N'),
(571, 'Reflections at Bukit Chandu', NULL, NULL, '118458', 'Pepys Rd', NULL, 'Located in a handsome colonial bungalow, the exhibits within depict Japanese invasion plans alongside British strategic maps, photographs and documents.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/reflections-at-bukit-chandu.jpg', NULL, 23651.9824, 29111.359, NULL, '31-K', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(572, 'Sri Mariamman Temple', NULL, NULL, '58793', 'South Bridge Road', NULL, 'Observe the majestic gopuram (gate tower), covered with figurative sculptures of gods and goddesses and mythological beasts, an easily recognisable landmark to generations of Hindu worshippers and Sin', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/places-of-worship/sri-mariamman-temple/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29333.9901, 29439.515, NULL, '244', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(573, 'Veeramakaliamman Temple', NULL, NULL, '218042', 'Serangoon Road', NULL, 'Step into one of the oldest temples in Singapore, the Veeramakaliamman Temple, which was built by Indian pioneers who came to work and live in this city.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/places-of-worship/veeramakaliamman-temple/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30133.6004, 32250.885, NULL, '141', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(574, 'Red Dot Design Museum', 'Red Dot Traffic Building', NULL, '69120', 'Maxwell Road', NULL, 'The second of its kind in the world, the Red Dot Design Museum is located in the Red Dot Traffic building, a grandiose colonial style building which used to be the headquarters of the Singapore Traffi', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/red-dot-design-museum.jpg', NULL, 29359.9236, 28936.654, NULL, '28', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(575, 'Thian Hock Kheng Temple', NULL, NULL, '68613', 'Telok Ayer St', NULL, 'The Thian Hock Keng Temple was erected in 1821 by seamen grateful for safe passage, and stands where Singapore&#39;s waterfront used to be, before the land was reclaimed.<br/>', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/places-of-worship/thian-hock-kheng-temple/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29587.1798, 29289.687, NULL, '158', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(576, 'Singapore Botanic Gardens', NULL, NULL, '259569', 'Cluny Road', NULL, 'A visit to Singapore would not be complete without seeing the grandeur of the internationally renowned Singapore Botanic Gardens.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/parks-and-gardens/singapore-botanic-gardens/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 25986.0214, 32555.187, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(577, 'The Southern Ridges', NULL, NULL, '99203', 'Mount Faber Road', NULL, 'Bridging the hills of Mount Faber Park, Telok Blangah Hill Park and Kent Ridge Park, the Southern Ridges combine invigorating exercise with spectacular views across Singapore.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/parks-and-gardens/the-southern-ridges/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 26456.8679, 28176.53, NULL, '109', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(578, 'Jamae Chulia Mosque', NULL, NULL, '58767', 'South Bridge Road', NULL, 'If you''re looking for something a little different, this is the mosque to visit. The site''s architectural style is eclectic, and the intricately designed palace fa''ade features tiny doors and cros', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/places-of-worship/jamae-mosque/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29351.2401, 29503.096, NULL, '218', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(579, 'The Substation', NULL, NULL, '179936', 'Armenian Street', NULL, 'Located in the city''s civic district, The Substation is Singapore''s first independent contemporary arts centre.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/the-substation.jpg', NULL, 29774.1409, 30766.968, NULL, '45', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(580, 'Chinese Garden', NULL, NULL, '619795', 'Chinese Garden', NULL, 'Conjure up the spirit of ancient China with a visit to the serene Chinese Garden. Modelled on the northern Chinese imperial style of landscaping and architecture, the garden was designed by renowned T', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/parks-and-gardens/chinese-garden/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 16610.4587, 35376.403, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(581, 'Buddha Tooth Relic Temple', NULL, NULL, '58840', 'South Bridge Road', NULL, 'The Buddha Tooth Relic Temple & Museum is a living cultural monument in the heart of Chinatown featuring exhibitions relating to various facets of religious arts and culture of Singapore.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/museums/buddha-tooth-relic-temple-and-museum1/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29225.8151, 29323.632, NULL, '288', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(582, '8Q SAM / Singapore Art Museum', NULL, NULL, '189555', 'Bras Basah Road', NULL, 'Formerly the St Joseph''s Institution, a premier boys'' school, and open since 1996, this state-of-the-art museum has amassed the largest public collection of modern and contemporary Southeast Asian art', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/sam-760x300.jpg', NULL, 30005.1349, 31067.479, NULL, '71', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(583, 'Victoria Theatre and Concert Hall', NULL, NULL, '179555', 'Empress Place', NULL, 'The Victoria Theatre and Concert Hall in the heart of Singapore''s Civic District is one of the most historically versatile buildings in all of Singapore.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/landmarks-and-memorials/history-of-victoria-theatre-and-victoria-concert-hall/_jcr_content/h', NULL, 30011.0848, 30106.949, NULL, '11', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(584, 'Lim Bo Seng Memorial', 'Esplanade Park', NULL, '0', '', NULL, 'Major-General Lim Bo Seng alias Tan Choon Lim was a prominent Hokkien businessman who undertook active leadership in anti-Japanese activities during World War II and is recognised as a local war hero.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/world-war-heritage-sites/Lim-Bo-Seng-Memorial/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30193.3804, 30099.431, NULL, NULL, 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(585, 'Esplanade - Theatres on the Bay', NULL, NULL, '38981', 'Esplanade Drive', NULL, 'Said to have an appearance similar the eye of a fly or a giant durian (a popular local fruit), you''ll just have to make a visit down to The Esplanade and decide for yourself.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/arts-and-entertainment/architecture/esplanade-theatres-on-the-bay/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30444.6754, 30251.695, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(586, 'Singapore Flyer', NULL, NULL, '39803', 'Raffles Avenue', NULL, 'Catch a glimpse of Singapore''s past, present and future onboard the Singapore Flyer, the world''s largest Giant Observation Wheel.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/singapore-flyer.jpg', NULL, 31286.262, 30210.4592, 'https://www.fool.sg/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/singapore-flyer.jpg', '30', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(587, 'Cenotaph', NULL, NULL, '0', 'Connaught Drive', NULL, 'The Cenotaph located along Connaught Drive at the Esplanade, facing the old Courthouse, was unveiled on 31 March 1922 by his Royal Highness the Prince of Wales, Edward VIII. It was erected as a memori', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/world-war-heritage-sites/Cenotaph/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30284.3039, 30297.692, NULL, NULL, 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(588, 'Civilian War Memorial', 'War Memorial Park', NULL, '0', 'Beach Road', NULL, 'Fondly referred to as ''The Chopsticks'', the Civilian War Memorial stands tall in the Civic District, and makes for picture-perfect opportunities.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/landmarks-and-memorials/civilian-war-memorial/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30370.4408, 30612.5, NULL, NULL, 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(589, 'Dalhousie Obelisk', NULL, NULL, '179555', 'Empress Place', NULL, 'It is believed that the design was modelled after ''Cleopatra''s Needle'' on the Thames Embankment in London, which might explain the British influences in its tall, needle-like architectural structure.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/arts-and-entertainment/architecture/dalhousie-obelisk/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30121.3759, 29939.871, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(590, 'Chinese Heritage Centre', NULL, NULL, '637721', 'Nanyang Dr', NULL, 'The Chinese Heritage Centre promotes understanding of the culture and traditions of Chinese communities overseas through the collection, preservation and display of artworks and other objects of Chine', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/chinese-heritage-centre.jpg', NULL, 11388.0187, 36225.446, 'https://c2.staticflickr.com/4/3275/2401761093_26902f8665.jpg', '12', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(591, 'The Arts House', NULL, NULL, '179429', 'Old Parliament Lane', NULL, 'The Arts House is not only Singapore''s oldest surviving government building, but also the only gazetted government building designated as a multi-disciplinary arts centre.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/the-arts-house.jpg', NULL, 29976.473, 30118.0065, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(592, 'Underwater World Singapore', NULL, NULL, '98969', 'Siloso Road', NULL, 'Embark on a spectacular underwater journey at Underwater World Singapore and Dolphin Lagoon in Sentosa Island Singapore. Find sharks, dugongs, jelly fishes and rare fishes and more.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/underwater-world.jpg', NULL, 25569.8565, 26758.967, NULL, '80', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(593, 'Peranakan Museum', NULL, NULL, '179941', 'Armenian St', NULL, 'Delve into the rich history, traditions and culture of early settlers in the former Straits Settlements of Singapore, Malacca and Penang and their links with other communities in Southeast Asia at the', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/peranakan-museum.jpg', NULL, 29766.3507, 30744.853, NULL, '39', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(594, 'Singapore Philatelic Museum', NULL, NULL, '179807', 'Coleman Street', NULL, 'Singapore Philatelic Museum celebrates everything about the world of stamps, from their unique background and connection to important historical moments in history, to stamp design and important colle', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/singapore-philatelic-museum.jpg', NULL, 29719.6094, 30575.674, NULL, '23B', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(595, 'Empress Place Building', NULL, NULL, '179555', 'Empress Place', NULL, 'View the exterior of the Empress Place Building with timber-louvered windows and a pitched clay tile roof. Inside, you''ll see stately rooms with high ceilings, handsome Doric columns and exquisite pla', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/arts-and-entertainment/architecture/empress-place-building/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30121.3759, 29939.871, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(596, 'National Museum of Singapore', NULL, NULL, '178897', 'Stamford Rd', NULL, 'The National Museum stands out as the architectural gem in the crown of Singapore''s museums. The recently renovated neo-classical building sits resplendent in the heart of the city as the largest muse', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/national-museum-of-singapore.jpg', NULL, 29695.1228, 30990.329, NULL, '93', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(597, 'Raffles Hotel', NULL, NULL, '189673', 'Beach Road', NULL, 'For an all-encompassing experience amid an old-world setting, make a visit to the Raffles Hotel and discover Singapore''s most famous heritage gem.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/arts-and-entertainment/architecture/raffles-hotel/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30349.5162, 30846.586, NULL, '1', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(598, 'Indian National Army Monument', 'Esplanade Park', NULL, '0', '', NULL, 'Located within the Esplanade Park, the Indian National Army Monument was erected in 1995 in commemoration of the 50th anniversary of the end of World War II and is part of a series of 11 World War II ', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/world-war-heritage-sites/Indian-National-Army-Monument/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 30325.8159, 30262.088, NULL, NULL, 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(599, 'Fort Siloso', NULL, NULL, '99981', 'Allanbrooke Road', NULL, 'Stop by Fort Siloso and be transported to a different time. A relic from World War II (WWII), this is Singapore''s only preserved coastal fort.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/culture-and-heritage/a-touch-of-history/landmarks-and-memorials/fort-siloso/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 25141.3799, 26847.099, NULL, '33', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(600, 'Singapore Coins and Notes museum', NULL, NULL, '59199', 'Pagoda St', NULL, 'Singapore Coins and Notes Museum is Singapore''s only museum dedicated to the showcase of currency.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/family-fun/science-and-discovery/singapore-coins-and-notes-museum/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29248.295, 29546.7728, NULL, '40', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(601, 'Adventure Cove', NULL, NULL, '98269', 'Sentosa Gateway', NULL, 'Feel the endless splashes of fun at Adventure Cove Waterpark'' Singapore, an aquatic adventure park located in Sentosa Singapore. Feel the adrenaline rush on several slides or chill out with friends at', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/family-fun/theme-parks/adventure-cove-waterpark/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 26585.4035, 26741.158, NULL, '8', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(602, 'S.E.A. Aquarium', NULL, NULL, '98269', 'Sentosa Gateway', NULL, 'Discover the world''s largest aquarium at S.E.A. Aquarium'' in Sentosa, Singapore. Immerse yourself in a magical marine world with over 800 marine animal species including manta rays, groupers and over ', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/wildlife-parks-and-attractions/sea-aquarium/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 26585.4035, 26741.158, NULL, '8', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(603, 'East Coast Park', NULL, NULL, '455486', '', NULL, 'The city''s most popular stretch of beach always buzzes with activity '' even when it''s not playing host to the wide spectrum of sporting events that grace its shores regularly, like the Singapore Marat', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/sports-and-recreation/recreation-spaces/East-Coast-Park/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 40029.5623, 32546.261, NULL, NULL, 'Tourist Attractions', 'E'),
(604, 'Fort Canning Park', NULL, NULL, '179618', '', NULL, 'Situated near the bustling Orchard Road shopping district, Fort Canning Park is a historical centre, a venue for performances and concerts, and a location where you can enjoy nature.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/parks-and-gardens/fort-canning-park/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29465.1957, 30891.142, NULL, NULL, 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(605, 'Gardens by the Bay', NULL, NULL, '18953', 'Marina Gardens Drive', NULL, 'Spanning 101 hectares, and just a five-minute walk from the downtown Marina Bay area, this superpark is home to over a quarter of a million rare plants...', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/stroll-among-trees/gardens-by-the-bay/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 32083.4584, 29137.119, NULL, '18', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(606, 'HortPark', NULL, NULL, '119578', 'Hyderabad Road', NULL, 'Learning and education are two of Hort Park''s main aims, and activities and events are held all year round to generate interest and enhance awareness of the area.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/parks-and-gardens/hort-park/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 24245.9469, 29063.361, NULL, '33', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(607, 'Mount Faber', NULL, NULL, '99203', 'Mount Faber Road', NULL, 'Take in sweeping views of the Singaporean Central Business District, have a meal at one of its food and retail outlets, and travel to Sentosa from the park. Mount Faber is certainly worth visiting, wh', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/nature-and-wildlife/parks-and-gardens/mount-faber/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 26462.6551, 28173.987, NULL, '109', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(608, 'Jurong Bird Park', NULL, NULL, '628925', 'Jurong Hill', NULL, 'Enjoy a peaceful stroll through the Jurong Bird Park, Singapore and catch a glimpse of over 380 bird species.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/jurong-bird-park.jpg', NULL, 13921.7094, 33371.469, NULL, '2', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(609, 'Images of Singapore', NULL, NULL, '99700', 'Imbiah Road', NULL, 'From Singapore''s Malaysian rule, British colonialism, Sir Stamford Raffles and or the Japanese occupation during the World War II, no historic stone is left unturned at Images of Singapore.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/images-of-singapore.jpg', NULL, 26295.5941, 26238.044, NULL, '40', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(610, 'Cable Car', NULL, NULL, '99203', 'Mount Faber Road', NULL, 'Gems in the Sky allows visitors to enjoy the scenic view of the lush greenery and stunning coastal sights during their 10 minute cable car ride to the tranquil Sentosa.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/cable-car.jpg', NULL, 26445.6277, 28211.804, NULL, '109', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(611, 'Science Centre Singapore', NULL, NULL, '609081', 'Science Center Road', NULL, 'The Science Centre Singapore exhibits cover practically everything related to science, including the human body, space, climate change, the solar system and much more.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/science-centre-singapore.jpg', NULL, 17180.5807, 35011.04, NULL, '15', 'Tourist Attractions', 'W'),
(612, 'Singapore Zoo', NULL, NULL, '729826', 'Mandai Lake Road', NULL, 'Explore regions around the Singapore Zoo formerly known as The Singapore Zoological Gardens. Singapore Zoo showcases a variety of wildlife and exotic vegetation as you marvel at the cotton-top tamarin', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/singapore-zoo.jpg', NULL, 23256.4707, 43013.397, NULL, '80', 'Tourist Attractions', 'N'),
(613, 'Marina Barrage', NULL, NULL, '18951', 'Marina Gardens Drive', NULL, 'Be captivated by the bright lights of the Singapore Flyer and the Central Business District skyline against the sky at sunset, reflected in the still waters of the Marina Barrage. This Reservoir in th', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/Marina-Barrage.jpg', NULL, 32182.9528, 29179.913, NULL, '8', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(614, 'Lau Pa Sat', NULL, NULL, '48582', 'Raffles Quay', NULL, 'Lau Pa Sat was subsequently converted into a famous gourmet paradise that has been gazetted as a national monument since 1973, and is famed for its octagonal building structure.', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/traveller/en/browse/see-and-do/arts-and-entertainment/architecture/lau-pa-sat/_jcr_content/html/image.img.png', NULL, 29907.7007, 29236.614, NULL, '18', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(615, 'Sculpture Square', NULL, NULL, '188977', 'Middle Road', NULL, 'The Sculpture Square now houses extensive gardens, shaded courtyards and a dramatic nine-metre high pillar-free exhibition hall (previously the chapel galley), ideal for large sculptures and three-dim', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/sculpture-square.jpg', NULL, 30094.6556, 31343.066, NULL, '155', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(616, 'MINT Museum of Toys', NULL, NULL, '188382', 'Seah Street', NULL, 'Young or old, if you''re a fan of toys then you are in for a treat at the Mint Museum. It boasts a world-class toy collection consolidated from more than 25 countries. It''s the perfect place for an avi', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/mint-museum-of-toys.jpg', NULL, 30365.9863, 30958.378, NULL, '26', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
(617, 'Changi Museum', NULL, NULL, '507707', 'Upper Changi Rd North', NULL, 'The Japanese interred the Allied prisoners of war at the now-demolished Changi Prison. Sign up for a Battlefield Tour to discover more about the fall of Singapore in WWII. The museum also serves as an', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/changi-museum.jpg', NULL, 43629.7174, 38246.592, NULL, '1000', 'Tourist Attractions', 'E'),
(618, 'Malay Heritage Centre', NULL, NULL, '198501', 'Sultan Gate', NULL, 'This centre occupies what was formerly the royal seat of the Malay sultans in Singapore. Built in 1842 by renowned architect George Coleman, it has been restored to its former glory, showcasing Malay ', 'http://www.yoursingapore.com/content/dam/yoursingapore/travellermasthead1c/images/malay-heritage-centre.jpg', NULL, 30953.8185, 31714.937, NULL, '85', 'Tourist Attractions', 'C'),
